---
layout: base.njk
---

<main class="w-full min-h-screen overflow-y-scroll flex flex-col items-center bg-[#1a1a1a]">
    <div class="max-w-[1550px] flex flex-col items-center ">
        <section id="reception" class="w-4/5 lg:w-[95%] my-36 ph:mt-4 ph:mb-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="flex flex-row md:flex-col lg:flex-wrap md:gap-10 justify-between w-full">
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-between select-none">
                    <div class="lg:w-[380px] md:w-fit">
                        <div class="font-sans font-bold text-balance bg-clip-text text-8xl mb-2 md:mb-0 text-ice-main 2xl:text-7xl md:text-8xl ph:text-7xl">
                            <span class="inline-flex flex-col overflow-hidden h-welcome-normal 2xl:h-welcome-xl md:h-welcome-normal ph:h-welcome-xl">
                                <ul class="block animate-text-slide text-left leading-tight [&_li]:block">
                                    <li>E aí?</li>
                                    <li>Bom Dia!</li>
                                    <li>Boa Tarde!</li>
                                    <li>Boa Noite!</li>
                                    <li aria-hidden="true">E aí?</li>
                                </ul>
                            </span>

                        </div>
                        <p class="font-roboto text-3xl ph:text-2xl ml-[0.05rem] text-ice-secondary">É um prazer te ter por aqui.</p>
                    </div>

                    <p class="font-roboto text-2xl ml-[0.05rem] text-ice-secondary opacity-40 md:hidden">Obs.: Esse terminal é interativo!</p>
                </div>

                <div id="terminal" class="w-[52%] md:w-full min-w-[320px] h-[32rem] rounded-lg bg-[#1c1d1f] border-[#3D4244] border-2 justify-self-center">
                    {% include "components/terminal.njk" %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="aboutme" class="w-4/5 lg:w-[95%] flex flex-col justify-between text-ice-main mb-20">
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col mb-14 md:mb-8 ph:mb-0">
                <div class="flex md:flex-col justify-between mb-8 ph:mb-6 ph:pr-10">
                    <div class="select-none md:mb-3">
                        <h1 class="font-roboto font-bold text-[5rem] lg:text-[4rem] md:text-7xl sm:text-5xl leading-tight">SOBRE MIM</h1>
                        <p class="font-roboto font-normal text-3xl md:text-2xl sm:text-xl ml-1">Quem é <span class="font-roboto font-bold">Gustavo Soares</span>?</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="w-[52%] md:w-full mt-2 ml-2 text-2xl 2xl:text-xl sm:text-base md:text-balance text-balance font-lato leading-normal">
                        <p class="mb-4 md:mb-3 ph:mb-1">Sempre fui curioso, gosto pensar na filosofia da educação continuada e com o universo dos códigos não seria diferente. <span class="font-lato font-bold">Todo dia a gente aprende uma coisa nova, né?</span></p>
                        <p>Desde 2020, meu primeiro contato com a computação como autodidata, me considero um entusiasta de linguagens, mas com foco inicial no desenvolvimento web, minha primeira área de estudo. Atualmente foco em <span class="text-emphasis">back-end</span> e <span class="text-emphasis">Data Science</span>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="w-full flex justify-between">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-lang md:grid-cols-lang-small ph:grid-rows-phone ph:grid-cols-none">
                    <div class="max-w-72 sm:max-w-full gap-x-8 gap-y-3 ph:gap-x-4 ph:gap-y-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center justify-self-center self-start md:self-center md:justify-self-center mt-2 ph:mt-0 md:mr-6 ph:mr-0 md:order-1">
                        {% for icon in icons.languages %}
                            <div class="w-24 h-24 lg:w-[4.5rem] lg:h-[4.5rem] sm:w-14 sm:h-14 ph:w-11 ph:h-11" aria-label="{{ icon.name }}">
                                {% svg icon.url %}
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>

                    <div class="w-[78%] md:w-4/5 ph:w-full ml-2 md:order-0 justify-self-end md:justify-self-start text-2xl 2xl:text-xl sm:text-base text-balance font-lato leading-normal ">
                        <p>Comecei em C e logo após o ciclo básico das linguagens imperativas, me foquei em aprender Javascript. Após Javascript, me tornei um nômade de linguagens, aprendendo, criando funcionalidades e me divertindo com as diferentes implementações e resoluções de problema. Em sua grande parte, foram linguagens voltadas para desenvolvimento web.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects" class="w-4/5 lg:w-[95%] flex flex-col justify-between text-ice-main mb-20">
            <div class="select-none mb-10 md:mb-3">
                <h1 class="font-roboto font-bold text-[5rem] lg:text-[4rem] md:text-7xl ph:text-5xl leading-tight">PROJETOS</h1>
                <p class="font-roboto tracking-tight text-3xl md:text-2xl sm:text-xl ml-1 opacity-40">Nem só de café vive Gustavo</p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full pl-2 sm:pl-0 antialiased columns-3 2xl:columns-2 md:columns-1 gap-x-6 lg:gap-x-5 text-ice-main">
                {% for p in languages.projects %}
                    <div class="relative glow-capture break-inside-avoid mb-8 lg:mb-6">
                        <div
                            class="w-96 2xl:w-full bg-zinc-900/50 border-2 border-white/5 rounded-xl p-10 flex flex-col items-start justify-center backdrop-blur-md glow glow:ring-4 glow:border-glow glow:ring-glow glow:bg-glow/[.15">
                            <div class="order-2">
                                <p class="opacity-50 font-lato font-normal">{{ p.tag }}</p>
                                <h2 class="font-roboto font-bold text-4xl tracking-tight mb-3 glow glow:text-glow/[.15]">{{ p.name }}</h2>
                                <div class="text-opacity-90 mb-10">
                                    <p class="font-lato text-lg">{{ p.description }}</p>
                                </div>

                                <a target="_blank" href="{{ p.link }}" class="font-semibold cursor-pointer px-6 bg-zinc-950/50 backdrop-blur-md py-3 rounded-xl text-white/90 border-2 border-white/10 mt-6 glow:ring-1 glow:border-glow glow:ring-glow">Repositório</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="glow-overlay" style="--color: var(--go);"></div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</main>